# Three internal capabilities are platform-ready for external monetization
@type: comparison

@compare:
  header: Capability | Internal Maturity | External Market | Pricing Model | Year 1 Revenue Potential
  row: Payment orchestration API | Production-grade, 99.98% uptime | 85K fintechs globally | Per-transaction ($0.008) | $22M
  row: Address and identity verification | Proprietary dataset, 94% match rate | Insurance, lending, logistics | Per-API call ($0.02–0.15) | $38M
  row: Real-time inventory signals | 12M SKU coverage, 15-minute latency | Retail, CPG, 3PL | Subscription + usage | $18M

@exhibit: Exhibit 2 — Capability Monetization Assessment
@source: BCG API platform analysis; comparable API pricing from Stripe, SmartyStreets, Spins, 2024

@notes: Payment orchestration is the highest-value capability but also the most regulated. Start with identity verification — faster to market, lower regulatory burden.

